Internship Programs
TruGeek is associated with reputed Global ITcompany to offers internship programs for interested IT students or individual professionals.

These are awarded after screening of suitable candidates. Students or professionals get the opportunity to work on real time projects, technology and development processes. This program enables the Intern to experience IT environment and enhance the skills.If candidates show exceptional talent and are hardworking, sincere and diligent, a job may be offered during the internship.•	The Internship program will be offered for 3 – 6 months for eligible candidates
Interested candidates can contact our Program Correspondent at TruGeek
